{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"9d88d117-0a8a-46da-ae6d-362647eb0e90","version":"2.1.49","gitBranch":"HEAD","agentId":"a83332f","slug":"buzzing-zooming-trinket","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"你是修复子代理。请在 `/c/Users/Administrator/legalflow-studio/apps/api` 中修复 Task3 的 2 个 Critical 问题：\n\n**问题1：用 Pydantic schema 替代裸 dict**\n修改 `app/api/projects.py`，使用已有的 `app/schemas/project.py` 中的 `ProjectCreate` 和 `ProjectOut`：\n\n```python\nfrom fastapi import APIRouter, status\nfrom app.schemas.project import ProjectCreate, ProjectOut\n\nrouter = APIRouter(prefix='/api/v1/projects', tags=['projects'])\n_store: list[dict] = []\n\n@router.post('', status_code=status.HTTP_201_CREATED, response_model=ProjectOut)\ndef create_project(payload: ProjectCreate):\n    item = {'id': len(_store) + 1, 'status': 'draft', **payload.model_dump()}\n    _store.append(item)\n    return item\n\n@router.get('', response_model=list[ProjectOut])\ndef list_projects():\n    return _store\n```\n\n**问题2：加强 test_list_projects 断言**\n修改 `tests/test_projects_api.py`，让每个测试独立，不依赖执行顺序：\n\n```python\nfrom fastapi.testclient import TestClient\nfrom app.main import app\nimport app.api.projects as projects_module\n\n\ndef setup_function():\n    projects_module._store.clear()\n\n\ndef test_create_project():\n    client = TestClient(app)\n    resp = client.post('/api/v1/projects', json={'name': '案件A', 'type': 'litigation'})\n    assert resp.status_code == 201\n    data = resp.json()\n    assert data['name'] == '案件A'\n    assert data['status'] == 'draft'\n    assert data['id'] == 1\n\n\ndef test_list_projects():\n    client = TestClient(app)\n    client.post('/api/v1/projects', json={'name': '案件B', 'type': 'consulting'})\n    resp = client.get('/api/v1/projects')\n    assert resp.status_code == 200\n    items = resp.json()\n    assert len(items) == 1\n    assert items[0]['name'] == '案件B'\n```\n\n修复后运行全部测试：\n```\ncd /c/Users/Administrator/legalflow-studio/apps/api\npython -m pytest tests/ -v\n```\n确认全部 PASS。\n\n提交：\n```\ncd /c/Users/Administrator/legalflow-studio\ngit add apps/api/app/api/projects.py apps/api/tests/test_projects_api.py\ngit commit -m \"fix: use pydantic schema validation and fix test isolation\"\n```\n\n输出：改动文件清单、测试结果、commit SHA。"},"uuid":"d3845025-00bf-49c3-bcc4-093092a9626d","timestamp":"2026-02-26T13:29:17.347Z"}
